rows.label: qst103617_msg0001
rows.name:
According to the senator, the capital's
defenses should be weak right now...
But we're almost wiped out!

rows.label: qst103617_msg0002
rows.name:
You... You've obstructed us every step
of the way...

rows.label: qst103617_msg0003
rows.name:
Wait! When you say "senator"...
You mean from the Imperial Senate?

rows.label: qst103617_msg0004
rows.name:
That's right. An imperial senator
by the name of Stulc.

rows.label: qst103617_msg0005
rows.name:
The soldiers we'd managed to gather
were already stretched to their limits
following Akatsuki's orders...

rows.label: qst103617_msg0006
rows.name:
And then you people wiped out all
of our leaders! Brionac is done for!

rows.label: qst103617_msg0007
rows.name:
It was none other than the senator
who told us where to find those
Brionac leaders.

rows.label: qst103617_msg0008
rows.name:
It was Akatsuki who chose the locations
for those transactions... This can only
mean... Ugh! Curse that beast!

rows.label: qst103617_msg0009
rows.name:
Akatsuki seemed to indicate that he
was with Lindwurm just before he
returned to his Crystal, did he not?

rows.label: qst103617_msg0010
rows.name:
Lindwurm!
So they were pulling the strings
the whole time!

rows.label: qst103617_msg0011
rows.name:
It sounds like both Akatsuki and
the senator may have been
members of Lindwurm.

rows.label: qst103617_msg0012
rows.name:
In which case, this raid is nothing
more than a diversion for him to
escape the Empire...

rows.label: qst103617_msg0014
rows.name:
It seems we were all led astray here.
Let us put aside our differences and...

rows.label: qst103617_msg0015
rows.name:
Silence!
No! How can you forget about our
objective so quickly?

rows.label: qst103617_msg0016
rows.name:
If there is any strength left in this
organization... We'll use it to destroy
the Empire's Blades!
